nodes.text: A male Yuuzhan Vong assassin who was apprenticed under Domain Shai was sent by Commander Harrar to attack the defector Elan as a means of convincing the New Republic of the authenticity of Elan's actions. He assaulted the New Republic Intelligence Service safehouse in New Nystao on Wayland as part of a Yuuzhan Vong raid. The assassin fought his way towards Elan, but was killed before he could complete his objective of slaying Elan.
